iKamasutra Privacy Policy
Your privacy is very important to us at SutraTaps and we appreciate that you are trusting us with your personal information. Here are a few of our fundamental privacy principles:
We aggregate and de-identify certain usage information about our users to use for business purposes.
We don’t collect or store any personally identifiable information about our users.
Our privacy policy (the “Privacy Policy”) explains the information we collect, how we use and share it, and your rights in connection to when you use our iKamasutra applications, software, websites, APIs and services (collectively, “iKamasutra”).
Unless indicated otherwise, this Privacy Policy does not apply to third-party products or services or the practices of companies that we do not own or control, including other companies you might interact with in or through iKamasutra.
Questions or comments about this Privacy Policy can be submitted by email to
privacy@ikamasutra.com
